comments: Butler (MIA) extends his arm forward and initiates contact with Towns' (MIN) front that affects his SQBR.
Towns (MIN) goes to, not through, Butler's (MIA) space and marginal contact occurs as the two come together prior to Towns' shot attempt.
Gobert (MIN) legally contests Adebayo's (MIA) jump shot attempt.
Richardson (MIA)briefly grasps and immediately releases Gobert's (MIN) uniform as he moves over the screen.
Richardson (MIA) legally contests Edwards' (MIN) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Butler (MIA) steps forward towards Towns (MIN) as they come together at the same spot, and marginal contact occurs as Towns passes the ball.
Conley (MIN) places his hand momentarily on Robinson's (MIA) side and marginal contact occurs as they move in the same direction.
Robinson (MIA) is already in Edwards' (MIN) path and does not deliver contact as the defenders switch.
Herro (MIA) is bracing for the contact from Alexander-Walker (MIN) and marginal contact occurs as Herro releases away towards the perimeter.
Adebayo (MIA) establishes himself in Alexander-Walker's (MIN) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Gobert (MIN) absorbs the contact from Richardson (MIA) during the pick, which is marginal.
Richardson (MIA) legally contests Edwards' (MIN) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Conley (MIN) goes to the floor on his own and not as a result of any contact from Butler (MIA) or Robinson (MIA).
Robinson (MIA) brings his hands towards Anderson (MIN) and marginal contact occurs as Anderson goes under the screen.
Anderson (MIN) stops short of Butler (MIA), and the marginal contact during the jump shot is caused by Butler as he leans forward towards the basket during his jump shot attempt.
Richardson (MIA) commits a take foul on Gobert (MIN).
Butler (MIA) and Alexander-Walker (MIN) mutually engage and immediately disengage as marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Richardson (MIA) moves his pivot foot prior to releasing his dribble.
Edwards (MIN) brings his arm toward Richardson's (MIA) path and marginal contact occurs as they come together at the same spot.
Herro (MIA) commits a take foul on Alexander-Walker (MIN).
Herro (MIA) moves towards Anderson (MIN) and marginal contact occurs as Herro leans toward the basket during his upward shooting motion.
